==English==
===Etymology===
Derives from the [[Beltway]], a highway that encircles Washington, D.C.

===Adjective===
'''[[inside]]-[[the]]-[[Beltway]]'''
# Of or relating to things that occur in [[Washington, D.C.]], usually in relation to [[United States]] national politics.
